import React from 'react'
import { Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import Boosts from './components/screens/Boosts/Boosts.jsx'
import Coins from './components/screens/Coins/Coins.jsx'
import Main from './components/screens/Main/Main.jsx'
import Referrals from './components/screens/Referrals/Referrals.jsx'
import Stats from './components/screens/Stats/Stats.jsx'
import Tasks from './components/screens/Tasks/Tasks.jsx'
import Wallet from './components/screens/Wallet/Wallet.jsx'
const App = () => {
	return (
		<>
			<Routes>
				<Route path='/' element={Main}></Route>
				<Route path='/coins' element={Coins}></Route>
				<Route path='/referrals' element={Referrals}></Route>
				<Route path='/stats' element={Stats}></Route>
				<Route path='/tasks' element={Tasks}></Route>
				<Route path='/wallet' element={Wallet}></Route>
				<Route path='/boosts' element={Boosts}></Route>
			</Routes>
		</>
	)
}
export default App
